## PART V -- RESTRICTIONS

### Section 13. Commercial Use

**13.1** Commercial use of the Work requires express written permission from Bel Esprit D'Accord Trust, except as provided in Section 13.2.

**13.2 Permitted Non-Commercial Uses:**

| Use | Permitted |
|-----|-----------|
| Study and analysis | Yes |
| Personal projects | Yes |
| Academic research | Yes |
| Non-commercial fork with attribution | Yes |
| Educational use | Yes |
| Open-source use (same license) | Yes |
| Internal company evaluation | Yes |
| Commercial deployment | No (requires permission) |
| SaaS integration | No (requires permission) |
| Revenue-generating service | No (requires permission) |

### Section 14. AI/ML Training

**14.1** The Work may not be used to train, fine-tune, evaluate, or benchmark any machine learning model, large language model, AI system, or neural network.

**14.2** This restriction applies regardless of whether the use is commercial or non-commercial.

**14.3** This restriction applies to the Sovereign Substrate, all Formed Works, and all Bound Works.

### Section 15. No Institutional Capture

**15.1** No institutional body may claim ownership of the Sovereign Substrate, claim exclusive licensing rights, or claim derivative rights without express written trust agreement with Bel Esprit D'Accord Trust.

**15.2** No government agency may use the Certification Marks to imply endorsement or certification of any product or service without explicit authorization.

